highlights.text: TonyPitony has the most spots on Viral Songs Italy. “CULO” is the highest at #1.
“Fiore mio” by Andrea Laszlo De Simone has been on Viral Songs Italy the longest, at 189 days straight.
“Better” by nimino and Manta is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Italy at #57.
“Un milione di anni” by The Zen Circus is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Italy, up 27 spots at #70.
